    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the FEA model ensemble meets the overall acceptance criteria for the COU. Quantitative output comparisons (E/uval < 1.96, QoI differences < 10%) were satisfied across all constructs and both laboratories. The assessment team assigned a High assurance level based on the majority of factors meeting required levels and the favorable output comparison results. Factors below required levels (Discretization error, Use error, Test conditions) were noted but judged by the team as not individually disqualifying given the overall favorable comparison results.",
